---
---

<section class="pricing section section-dark" id="pricing">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="label">Deine Workspace-Optionen</p>
    <h2 class="pricing-title">Feste Plätze, echte Community</h2>
    <p class="pricing-sub">All-Inclusive-Mieten inkl. Strom, High-Speed Internet, Reinigung der Open Spaces und moderner Möblierung. Bei uns gibt es keine anonymen Flex-Desks &ndash; wir setzen auf feste Arbeitsplätze für eine konstante, vertraute Community.</p>

    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <!-- Shared Space -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="card-badge card-badge-avail">Noch 5 Plätze</div>
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="/images/coworking-space.jpg" alt="Fix-Desk im Shared Space" />
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-body">
          <h3>Shared Space (Fix-Desks)</h3>
          <p class="card-desc">Ein fester Schreibtisch mit Bürostuhl im Gemeinschaftsbüro für maximale Dynamik und Community-Austausch.</p>
          <div class="pricing-header">
            <span class="price">CHF 199.–</span>
            <span class="price-period">/Monat</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="features">
            <li>Fester Schreibtisch &amp; Bürostuhl</li>
            <li>1 Monat Kündigungsfrist</li>
            <li>Kaution: 1 Monatsmiete</li>
            <li>Strom, Internet, Reinigung inkl.</li>
            <li>Community &amp; Networking</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#mietgesuch" class="btn btn-outline-light pricing-btn">Anfragen</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Montalin -->
      <div class="pricing-card featured">
        <div class="card-badge">Letztes Büro!</div>
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="/images/office-montalin.jpg" alt="Einzelbüro Blick Montalin" />
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-body">
          <h3>Einzelbüro &laquo;Blick Montalin&raquo;</h3>
          <p class="card-sub">16.5 m²</p>
          <p class="card-desc">Komplett möbliert, ideal für tiefen Fokus und repräsentative Aufgaben. Geniesse den Blick auf den Hausberg.</p>
          <div class="pricing-header">
            <span class="price">CHF 719.–</span>
            <span class="price-period">/Monat</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="features">
            <li>Komplett möbliert &amp; bezugsbereit</li>
            <li>3 Monate Kündigungsfrist</li>
            <li>Kaution: 1 Monatsmiete</li>
            <li>Sitzungszimmer inklusive</li>
            <li>Maximale Privatsphäre</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#mietgesuch" class="btn btn-primary pricing-btn">Anfragen</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Oberland -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="/images/office-oberland.jpg" alt="Einzelbüro Blick Oberland" />
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-body">
          <h3>Einzelbüro &laquo;Blick Oberland 1&raquo;</h3>
          <p class="card-sub">14.5 m²</p>
          <p class="card-desc">Das Premium-Upgrade: Dein privates Büro mit atemberaubender Aussicht auf die Bündner Bergwelt.</p>
          <div class="pricing-header">
            <span class="price">CHF 709.–</span>
            <span class="price-period">/Monat</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="features">
            <li>Komplett möbliert &amp; bezugsbereit</li>
            <li>3 Monate Kündigungsfrist</li>
            <li>Kaution: 1 Monatsmiete</li>
            <li>Sitzungszimmer inklusive</li>
            <li>Panorama-Bergblick</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#mietgesuch" class="btn btn-outline-light pricing-btn">Anfragen</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="pricing-note">Bei 2er-Belegung der Einzelbüros gelten leicht angepasste Konditionen. Parkplätze können für CHF&nbsp;99.–/Monat dazu gemietet werden.</p>

    <div class="early-adopter">
      <div class="ea-content">
        <div class="ea-label">Early Adopter Deal</div>
        <h3>Vorbezug ab 1. April</h3>
        <p>Starte mit uns in die Soft-Launch-Phase vor der grossen Eröffnung im Juni. Nutze unser exklusives Probeabo und erhalte <strong>20&nbsp;% Rabatt</strong> auf die endgültigen Preise, um unser FactorAI-Ökosystem direkt vor Ort in Ruhe kennenzulernen!</p>
      </div>
      <a href="#mietgesuch" class="btn btn-primary">Deal sichern</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .label {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .pricing-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .pricing-sub {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .pricing-card {
    background: var(--color-dark-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-dark-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .pricing-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(9,138,203,0.3);
  }
  .pricing-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  .card-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    right: 16px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .card-badge-avail {
    background: rgba(9,138,203,0.85);
  }
  .card-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .pricing-body {
    padding: 28px;
  }
  .pricing-body h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  .card-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .card-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .pricing-header {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-dark-border);
  }
  .price {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  .price-period {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }
  .features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .features li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .features li::before {
    content: '✓';
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .pricing-btn {
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .pricing-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    margin-top: 24px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .early-adopter {
    margin-top: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 40px;
    background: rgba(9,138,203,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(9,138,203,0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 40px 48px;
  }
  .ea-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .ea-content h3 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .ea-content p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    max-width: 560px;
  }
  .ea-content strong {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .early-adopter .btn {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .pricing-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 440px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pricing-title { font-size: 28px; }
    .early-adopter {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 28px 24px;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .early-adopter .btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>
